rows.label: qst201409_msg0001
rows.name: No one's coming by...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0002
rows.name:
Waiting is no good. Let's go
find someone to judge us.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0003
rows.name: Oh, are you two out for a walk as well?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0004
rows.name:
"As well"? So you were out
for a walk, Kagutsuchi?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0005
rows.name: Yes.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0006
rows.name:
It's my nightly routine to take a
stroll in the night air before bed.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0007
rows.name: Oh, I didn't know.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0008
rows.name: Kagutsuchi, I have a favor to ask.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0009
rows.name:
Could you chat with Hikari
and me, and judge which of
us has more Girl Power?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0010
rows.name:
Ah, that competition... If
you're fine with me, then yes.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0011
rows.name: Thank you!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0012
rows.name:
Since we have Kagutsuchi
here, why don't we talk
about beauty and skincare?

rows.label: qst201409_msg0027
rows.name: Fine. I'm confident I'll win this!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0013
rows.name:
I have a proper skincare
routine every day...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0014
rows.name:
And I practice cute poses
in front of the mirror!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0015
rows.name:
I'm not sure the posing
practice is related to beauty.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0016
rows.name:
Besides, if one is truly cute, one
is always cute without practice.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0017
rows.name:
I am cute just by being here, so
there is no need for such effort.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0018
rows.name:
I am making an effort to
make myself even cuter!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0019
rows.name:
I am a bundle of ambition,
always aiming higher!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0020
rows.name:
It's true that aiming
high is important...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0021
rows.name:
But if you two are competing
like this, you both still
have a long way to go.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0022
rows.name:
Truly beautiful people must
behave with a grace and composure
that befits their appearance.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0023
rows.name: Therefore, I declare this match a draw.

rows.label: qst201409_msg0024
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst201409_msg0025
rows.name: No way...

rows.label: qst201409_msg0026
rows.name:
If you wish to speak of beauty,
come back when you have matured
more spiritually.
